🚨 𝐔𝐏𝐃𝐀𝐓𝐄: Xavi Simons, ready to 𝐥𝐞𝐚𝐯𝐞 RB Leipzig in the summer transfer window! 💣👀

Plan confirmed as reported in the recent months, he’s ready for new chapter… with top Premier League clubs and Bayern all attentive to his situation for next weeks.

RB Leipzig, aware of the player’s plan to try new club with talks and negotiations to follow from this month with his brother Faustino Simons taking care of deal.
